# List of files to be linked from arcs/src to arcs/build.
# Blank lines and lines beginning with a hash are ignored.
# Note that only full-line comments are supported.
# One file per line. Every file must begin with `src/`.
# The name reflects the fact that we want to reduce and eventually eliminate
# this list, by converting the js to ts, by moving the file out of src, or by
# adjusting the dependency to work without the link.
# Creating the set of links is idempotent, but add-only (old links are not 
# removed), so it is important to run `tools/sigh clean` every time lines are
# removed from this file.

